手比多個保障？<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下啲大陸機如果刷左custom rom(例如CM果啲)係咪就可以唔洗接受國家級雲備份服務?<br />\n因為啲大陸機真係設計上進取過好多所謂大廠好多,而且價錢又平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n=========================<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> iPhone上面既notes app可以點樣migrate去Android同埋有冇邊隻Android app有同note差唔多既功能?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩年代 真係比班idog洗晒腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"我見 老人家部AN機 周不時個chrome會彈啲noti廣告出黎<br />\n<br />\n但iOS好似冇呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"所以話IOS比弱智用 成因係鬼關AN機事"},{"pid":"ba9d70dbe581076366dbbb2676fb33f455c10101","tid":915284,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"598859754f06a46dfd0cf50a05b61a852d29f062","tid":915284,"uid":117316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"pixel 3好似話入面整左粒晶片專for保安?<br />\n<br />\n其實就算所有野都用official apps<br />\n主要係怕有時唔小心click左d有料links<br />\nios起碼仲未需要擔心<br />\n之前d bug最多都係講左click左果d links會死機"},{"pid":"1993ace697d35777c9c81fe611ae29b7c0824435","tid":915284,"uid":61022,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T21:24:13.000Z","msg":"雙修<br />\n只用iOS 上 銀行網"},{"pid":"9c5c5836507324563d6daaafe3a71039e5884e91","tid":915284,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T21:44:06.000Z","msg"